Explanation:
- The Spring Framework Remote Code Execution vulnerability is fixed by updating the parent's version to 3.0.6.
- The Log4j Remote Code Execution (Log4Shell) vulnerability is fixed by updating the version of log4j-core to 2.17.1.
- The Denial of Service (DoS) vulnerability is fixed by updating the version of jackson-databind to 2.13.2.2.
- The Apache Commons Collections Deserialization Vulnerability is fixed by updating the version of commons-collections4 to 4.4 and excluding commons-collections6.

